title: #92Noon! Henderson/Sinykin/Neal/Russo
description: Gabe Henderson of the Vikings Entertainment Network joins the show to break down the Vikings potential 53 man roster, Dave Sinykin and Lavelle E Neal take on PA in the annual Great NFC North Debate, and Michael Russo stops by for some Wild talk.
